WEBVTT

31:35.410 --> 31:36.650 line:80%
Those scholars

31:37.140 --> 31:39.000 line:80%
say he is cold-blooded and cruel.

31:39.430 --> 31:41.400 line:80%
But what about the soldiers and civilians

31:41.400 --> 31:43.770 line:80%
